{
  "version": 2,
  "builds": [
    {
      "src": "**/*.html",
      "use": "@vercel/static"
    }
  ],
  "routes": [
    {
      "src": "/(.+)",
      "dest": "/$1/index.html"
    }
  ]
}
```

Dann **„Commit changes"** klicken und 1–2 Minuten warten bis Vercel neu deployt.

